OL,3,CStarmer says there was only 'everyday
OL,4,Cpressure' to clear Mandelson
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FSir Keir Starmer has said there was
OL,8,Fonly the "everyday pressure of
OL,9,FGovernment" to clear Lord Peter
OL,10,FMandelson as ambassador to Washington
OL,11,Famid the ongoing row over his vetting
OL,12,Ffor the position.
OL,14,FThe Prime Minister stood by his
OL,15,Fdecision to sack former Foreign Office
OL,16,Fchief Sir Olly Robbins and maintained
OL,17,Fit was wrong for the veteran civil
OL,18,Fservant not to have told Sir Keir that
OL,19,Fthe peer was cleared against the
OL,20,Frecommendation of UK Security Vetting
OL,21,F(UKSV).
OL,26,@pD@JOUqD@KO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G1/9
