OL,24,ANext Page BNat News CNat TV FClean Feed
FL,305,300,200,140,000,100
PN,30402
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777179877
OL,3,CStarmer says there was only 'everyday
OL,4,Cpressure' to clear Mandelson
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FSir Olly said earlier this week there
OL,8,Fwas an "atmosphere of pressure" and
OL,9,F"constant chasing" from Downing Street
OL,10,Fwhile the checks were taking place, to
OL,11,Fwhich the Prime Minister responded
OL,12,Fthat "no pressure existed whatsoever".
OL,14,FSpeaking to The Sunday Times, he made
OL,15,Fa distinction between "different types
OL,16,Fof pressure".
OL,18,F"There's pressure ` 'Can we get this
OL,19,Fdone quickly?' ` which is not an
OL,20,Funusual pressure. That is the everyday
OL,21,Fpressure of Government," he said.
OL,26,@pD@HOUpD@_O]qD@AOUqD@RO]tD@FOUtD@eO]wD@
OL,26,AWOUxD@LO]zD@AOU}D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G2/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
