CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777179877
OL,3,CStarmer says there was only 'everyday
OL,4,Cpressure' to clear Mandelson
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FHe said a pressure "essentially, to
OL,8,Fdisregard the security vetting element
OL,9,Fand give clearance" would be something
OL,10,Fdifferent, and that Sir Olly "was
OL,11,Freally clear in his mind that wasn't
OL,12,Fpressure that was put on him".
OL,14,FMPs on the Foreign Affairs Committee
OL,15,Fsaid UK Security Vetting (UKSV), the
OL,16,Fagency responsible for checks on
OL,17,Fcandidates for sensitive posts, had
OL,18,Fticked two red boxes on Lord
OL,19,FMandelson's form ` meaning they had
OL,20,F"high concern" and recommended
OL,21,F"clearance denied or withdrawn".
OL,26,@oD@TOUqD@SO]rD@^OUtD@]O]|D@AOU|D@NO]}D@
OL,26,AAOU}D@_O]
