OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777179877
OL,3,CStarmer says there was only 'everyday
OL,4,Cpressure' to clear Mandelson
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FSir Keir said: "When there's a double
OL,8,Fred flag not to give clearance and
OL,9,F(showing) high concern, then I'm
OL,10,Fsorry. I'm sorry.
OL,12,F"But I do not accept the argument that
OL,13,Fthat is something which should not be
OL,14,Ftold to the Prime Minister."
OL,16,FHe said it was a "fundamental matter"
OL,17,Fto have told him about the vetting,
OL,18,Fnot just at the time of the
OL,19,Fappointment, but also later on when he
OL,20,Fwas speaking in public saying Lord
OL,21,FMandelson had been given clearance.
OL,26,@oD@POUtD@AOUvD@\O]xD@ROUxD@eO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G4/9
