SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777179877
OL,3,CStarmer says there was only 'everyday
OL,4,Cpressure' to clear Mandelson
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FSir Keir rejected a suggestion he
OL,8,Fcould have been more curious about the
OL,9,Fclearance.
OL,11,FHe said: "When I'm told there's
OL,12,Fsecurity clearance, should I go back
OL,13,Fand quiz officials and say: 'Are you
OL,14,Ftelling me the truth?'"
OL,16,FThe Prime Minister said this week that
OL,17,Fany claims he misled Parliament had
OL,18,Fbeen put to bed by Sir Olly's evidence
OL,19,Fto the Foreign Affairs Committee.
OL,26,@sD@JOUvD@WO]
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G5/9
