PN,30406
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777179877
OL,3,CStarmer says there was only 'everyday
OL,4,Cpressure' to clear Mandelson
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FBut questions over the vetting scandal
OL,8,Fwill carry on into next week when Sir
OL,9,FKeir's former chief of staff Morgan
OL,10,FMcSweeney is due to appear before the
OL,11,Fsame committee of MPs.
OL,13,FForeign Office official Ian Collard,
OL,14,Fwho Sir Olly said briefed him on the
OL,15,Fvetting findings that deemed Lord
OL,16,FMandelson a borderline case and leaned
OL,17,Ftowards recommending that clearance be
OL,18,Fdenied, will give written evidence.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G6/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
