CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F304A1777179877
OL,3,CStarmer says there was only 'everyday
OL,4,Cpressure' to clear Mandelson
OL,5,Cappointment
OL,7,FSir Keir has faced calls to resign
OL,8,Famid the fallout from the Lord Peter
OL,9,FMandelson vetting scandal and Cabinet
OL,10,Fdivisions are said to have emerged
OL,11,Fover his handling of the process,
OL,12,Fincluding his decision to sack Sir
OL,13,FOlly.
OL,15,FHe is also facing further pressure as
OL,16,FMay's elections for English councils
OL,17,Fand the Scottish and Welsh parliaments
OL,18,Floom.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G7/9
OL,2,W/*%+,"-/.!,.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
